    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "D333.5EX",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "3 September 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Cooperation of FBI with AAF on Investigations of \"Flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Disc\" Incidents.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "TO: Commanding Genrals, First, Second, Fourth, Tenth, Eleventh",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "and Fourteenth Air Forces",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "ATTENTION: Assistant Chief of Staff, A-2",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "1. The Federal Bureau of Investigation has agreed to assist Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Force Intelligence personnel in the investigation of \"flying disc\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "incidents in order to quickly and effectively rule out what are pranks",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "and to concentrate on what appears to be a genuine incident.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "2. It was the original intent of the AC/AS-2, Headquarters,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Army Air Forces that whereas the ADC Air Forces would interview respon-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "sible observers whose names would be furnished by AAF, the FBI would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "investigate incidents of so called \"discs\" being found on the ground.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The services of the FBI were enlisted in order to relieve the numbered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Air Forces of the task of tracking down all the many instances which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "turned out to be ash can covers, toilet seats and whatnot.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "3. It is requested that each A-2 informally coordinate and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "cooperate with the FBI, generally keeping the FBI informed of any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "proposed calls that intelligence personnel will make on this subject.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Very shortly, with the separation of the AAF from the War Department,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "a firm policy will be established to clarify the liaison arrangements",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "between A-2's and FBI Special Agents. Presently, it is considered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "inadvisable to promulgate a formal interim policy -- only to have it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "replaced in a month or so by another.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "BY COMMAND OF LIEUTENANT GENERAL STRATEMEYER:",
